{"tid":277893,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插熔岩]部腦唔知咩問題","createTime":"2017-06-10T04:26:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T06:27:20.000Z","uid":45047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"678c85f47ecd06a38962d649e29dedae621530a0","tid":277893,"uid":45047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:26:19.000Z","msg":"部機砌咗三幾年<br />\n因為有啲問題所以我冰封咗佢唔用算<br />\n但呢排想賣走啲件換返啲錢算<br />\n所以想知究竟有乜問題<br />\n話說部腦每次開完一個鐘之後就會freeze咗<br />\n但係又冇藍mon或者黑哂書面<br />\n係純粹所有功能用唔到<br />\n啲windows仲可以㩒出㩒入<br />\n但係㩒start會出唔到start screen<br />\n如果係打緊機嘅就會save唔到嘢<br />\n但一開機嗰陣就所有嘢正常操作<br />\n係用咗一個鐘之後就噉<br />\n重裝過幾次windows都係噉<br />\n我懷疑係隻ssd問題<br />\n因為都用咗四五年，舊機帶落嚟嘅<br />\n但用disk programme check又話隻ssd係健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"200fdb8ffffeb72fbe4a60de85d9dd74420b468b","tid":277893,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:25:08.000Z","msg":"買隻ssd試下咪知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c42464121eb05a0d2abebd34b06656e688694661","tid":277893,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"windows可以㩒出㩒入<br />\n又freeze左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8123bd4e989e1be835ab4984aa3ed9e3baa190f","tid":277893,"uid":45047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>windows可以㩒出㩒入<br />\n又freeze左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好難形容<br />\nmouse仲郁到<br />\n但部機就好似停咗運作噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}